Bait
''' Bait''' is [[Troll]] food. It is what a troll deposits when they want responses. Not all bait is as simple as posting a [[Hitler]] image to a Jewish community. Well-crafted bait might take weeks of build-up including [[sock puppet|sock puppets]] and other subterfuge. 


==Preparation==

~
Gather the following [[shit|ingredients]].
[[image: MeatBait.gif|thumb|A steal at only 60 [[jew golds|Rupees]].]]

* 1 community/forum/imageboard full of touchy, emotionally vulnerable targets ([[Furries]] work best for this recipe).
* At least 3 [[sock puppet]] accounts on chosen website.
* Some fucking imagination.
* [[Alcohol]] or other drug of choice for garnish.
* 1/2 cup of distilled malice.

~
While gently kneading the ingredients in a large glass [[thread]], pay attention to the noises coming from the targets. If they know you're a [[troll]], then [[you are doing it wrong]].

~
After all the ingredients are thoroughly mixed, place in the [[holocaust|oven]], setting it to Jew. Watch for as long as possible.

~
Some re-mixing may be needed if the [[lulz]] begin to drop to a soil boil. Just poke it with an additional [[sock puppet]] to stir things up again.

~
Serves 8.


The people are loosing their moral while becoming modern. The society needs to be attentive that moral value.
